"strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Finally, use the <b>Allocation</b> button to assign the MO to the <b>Sales "
"Order</b>."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, utilisez le bouton <b>Allocation</b> pour lier l’OF à la <b>commande "
"client</b>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow your equipment status and maintenance with the <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Suivez l'état et la maintenance de votre équipement avec <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">l'application Maintenance</font></strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow your planning and keep track of worked time in the <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning &amp; Timesheets Apps</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Suivez votre planning et gardez une trace de votre temps de travail dans les "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">applications Planification et "
"Feuilles de temps</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
